
$Header$


Naming Conventions:


Classes:
  list of words, no space, capitalize each word, including first word
  Examples:

        GaussianMixture
        Discrete1DPDF - discrete 1Dim PDF
        DiagonalGaussian
	FooBar

Member Variables, member functions.
  list of words, no space, capitalize each word, not including first word
  Examples:

       gaussianMixture
       diagonalGaussian
       fooBar       


Global Variables: (+static members, etc.)






Local Variables:
   lower case, list of words, separated by '_' character.


   








